{"type": "article", "id": 17041, "title": "PONS 皮包", "description": "", "date": "2015-11-04T07:10:15Z", "super_tag": "", "tags": [], "category": 25, "column": 28, "author": 161922, "comment_count": 1, "praise_count": 45, "image": "img/article/article_show/20160606135730FLHgDmG17u6zh2XZ.jpg", "contents": "\n\n<p>\r\n\t这个皮包来自匈牙利设计师 Agnes Kovacs，她从桥梁建筑中吸取灵感，用木制的横杆连接两边皮料，也平衡了包上的折纹，显得简洁优雅，有建筑的美感。桥梁本身是用来沟通连接的，坚固而传统的木质材料与柔软而时尚的皮料之间正好构成一种反差，让这款包显得独特。<a href=\"http://www.agneskovacs.hu/termek-kategoria/noi/\" target=\"_blank\">点击这里可以查看更多信息。</a>\r\n</p>\r\n<p style=\"text-align:center;\">\r\n\t<img src=\"img/uploads/20160726144245qZtcoLD38uypVAlX.jpg\" width=\"555\" height=\"741\" title=\" \" alt=\" \" data-ratio=\"1.33513514\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</p>\r\n<p style=\"text-align:center;\">\r\n\t<img src=\"img/uploads/201607261442460RCKGHM1Xd7z8ZE5.jpg\" width=\"555\" height=\"741\" title=\" \" alt=\" \" data-ratio=\"1.33513514\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</p>\r\n<p style=\"text-align:center;\">\r\n\t<img src=\"img/uploads/20160726144246lApaCskTbY1cB7XH.jpg\" width=\"800\" height=\"635\" title=\" \" alt=\" \" data-ratio=\"0.79375\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</p>\r\n<p style=\"text-align:center;\">\r\n\t<img src=\"img/uploads/20160726144247GgChmcPBakl5ojE7.jpg\" width=\"800\" height=\"530\" title=\" \" alt=\" \" data-ratio=\"0.6625\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</p>\n\n\n\n"}